name: colors of time hyacinth
description:
digital art based on my own macrophotography
4000 x 4000 px jpg
i'm fascinated by blossoms and their decay is astonishing. some colors get more intense, because they concentrate of course during the loss of water. but they also are very stable when the blossoms are kept dry. i love to work with this aspect of their life.

i'm on HEN since 6 month now.i want to celebrate this with this edition of 182 hyacinths :)
